text: Bulandi () is a 1990 Pakistani Urdu movie. It was directed by Javed Fazil and produced by Aslam Butt. The movie is also known as Vantage. Bulandi is a Lollywood movie starring by Nadeem, Samina Peerzada, Reema Khan, Shan, Madhiha Shah, Reema and Shaan. Category:1990s Pakistani movies Category:1990 movies Category:Urdu-language movies
title: Bulandi (1990 movie)
